{"tid":2210020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「前梁粉」亞視前主播盧瑞盛家中猝逝終年63歲　曾造訪唐英年地下酒倉最經典","createTime":"2020-09-20T05:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T11:23:51.000Z","uid":128369,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"b83c0b34e60681de66dd0143db4dab22c2f160ea","tid":2210020,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"曾在麗的電視新聞部擔任主播、現任南華傳媒董事總經理的盧瑞盛，周六（19日）突然傳出於跑馬地家中猝逝，終年63歲。他的好友車淑梅昨晚在facebook轉發消息悼念故友。車淑梅透露他們6月時一同植樹，盛贊盧瑞盛的為人，是一個好好先生，指他永遠懂得欣賞別人，對於他的離世感到好可惜。<br />\n盧瑞盛是資深新聞從業員，畢業於樹仁新聞系，其後加入麗的電視（亞視前身）新聞部，在麗的、亞視任職超過20年，主要工作擔任新聞主播、《時事追擊》主持等。他又曾訪問唐英年並參觀對方的地下酒倉。他於2000年離開亞視，與黃毓民創辦《Cyber日報》，2001年創辦《快周刊》。他曾擔任RoadShow行政總裁，2018年出任南華傳媒董事總經理。盧瑞盛亦曾為梁振英參選特首時助選，曾為梁振英主持地區論壇工作，在梁振英當選特首後，盧瑞盛獲委任為中央政策組特邀顧問等職務。<br />\nSource:hk01"},{"pid":"a8141d92a52bbb59810cbc2f780688907bb8f37e","tid":2210020,"uid":335434,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/4/41/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%86%8D%E5%B2%80%E6%AE%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%961.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200522053055\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F4%2F41%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25B2%2580%25E6%25AE%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%259B%259F%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%259C%25961.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20200522053055&h=c05739d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/12/香港再岀殯大聯盟改圖2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F12%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%86%8D%E5%B2%80%E6%AE%AF%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E6%94%B9%E5%9C%962.jpg&h=3b2f2828&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f90ce087321ba77b41d21168f5693612d3e94113","tid":2210020,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔知乜水"},{"pid":"59a66b2d46f693c28b0ac8de85dd684ffe1d231d","tid":2210020,"uid":200070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:50:27.000Z","msg":"哭能左 rap"},{"pid":"74500934d7f15349aa9a35206f559219407b7a42","tid":2210020,"uid":140218,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:52:42.000Z","msg":"盧瑞盛於2006年3月，曾在跑馬地山村道住所發生墮樓意外，據知事發時盧瑞盛因收回一張放在冷氣機頂部的地氈，而爬出六樓住處的窗口，但卻失重心從窗口墮下，其間幸被多組晾衫架阻擋卸去衝力，故他最後僅雙腳、腰及臀部受傷，經治療後康復。不過就因墮樓途中被晾衫架阻擋，衣服被扯脫，全身只剩下一條內褲。"},{"pid":"d4e149dd2c0b091d2bf9ccbab5ba4461e7ef3b42","tid":2210020,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f90ce087321ba77b41d21168f5693612d3e94113","tid":2210020,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔知乜水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:53:01.000Z","msg":"Roadshow嗰ceo <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvreS0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvreS0w.jpg&h=8a99d02a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/170928/「梁粉」前主播全力助選有回報？%E3%80%80盧瑞盛洪綺敏/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F170928%2F%E3%80%8C%E6%A2%81%E7%B2%89%E3%80%8D%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%BB%E6%92%AD%E5%85%A8%E5%8A%9B%E5%8A%A9%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%EF%BC%9F%25E3%2580%2580%E7%9B%A7%E7%91%9E%E7%9B%9B%E6%B4%AA%E7%B6%BA%E6%95%8F%2F&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2OmuNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=b3f1c80c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/170928/「梁粉」前主播全力助選有回報？%E3%80%80盧瑞盛洪綺敏/</a>"},{"pid":"9d8e95d2dd9d47591c4bedc89d634c187d87489b","tid":2210020,"uid":103050,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於用得著"},{"pid":"53c882187051c40a4cfc3fcad3052f8e6f8b8f00","tid":2210020,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T06:53:57.000Z","msg":"曾為梁振英主持地區論壇工作，在梁振英當選特首後，盧瑞盛獲委任為中央政策組特邀顧問等職務<b